Hi everyone!

My matches in the Inter-team championship 1700-1800 are coming to a close.  I was certainly pleased with this result.  My opponent's rating at the start of the game was 1686 so I got 7.4 points out of this.  Normally it is me that has passivitis but somehow I inflicted the malady on my opponent.  I am black and I end up playing the closed Ruy Lopez.

29. ......... Nc5 - I move my knight off the rim.  True that knight can be exchanged but as per my previous note, I am a piece up and want to exchange my opponent down to nothing.  Fou Lenoir can always act as a giant pawn here and hold up that e5 passer. My opponent decided to move his lsb instead.
